### Wholesaler Inventory Management API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Wholesaler's Inventory
GET {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Inventory Stock and Minimum Order Quantity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/inventory/update/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity_in_stock": 1000,
  "minimum_order_quantity": 50
}

### Restock Inventory (Add Stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/inventory/restock/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 500
}

### Get Wholesaler's Sales Orders (to retailers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/orders/sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Sales Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/analytics/sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Order Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "shipped"
}

### Update Order Status to Delivered
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/wholesalers/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "delivered"
}
